data.description: This beautiful home has an upgraded double-door entry,  open kitchen with oversized island, sink in island with soft touch faucet,  two countertop  windows that bring in brightness to your work area, butler’s pantry, huge pantry with a window, built in cabinets in Laundry room, and utility sink in garage.  It also has two primary bedrooms, each has en suite baths  with double vanities and separate showers.  The primary bath downstairs has an upgraded extended shower.  There are two half baths, one downstairs and one upstairs to accommodate guests in the game room or media room.  The media room has been upgraded with a wet bar, bar counter, built in cabinets, and a wine cooler. Garage entrance is right swing.
